{
  "stem": "3346.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you know, even if you live scared and even if you don't have enough food, you still need something more than just waking up, and going to sleep, and going to work, and waking up, and going to sleep.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because otherwise, people wouldn't care whether they sur-- whether they survived or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, and then the rest of it is more, more or less heresay, really.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I told you, my father was sent to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wasn't-- he was with us in Brunnlitz ever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that's only an aside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We heard that the Russians were very close and the Germans were leaving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But apparently, a short time before, the SS commander told Schindler that he wasn't going to leave any Jew alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was going to take us all to the woods there and have us shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I know that Oskar-- I don't know what Oskar did to persuade him not to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the last memory I have of the Germans was they were running away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were leaving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they were still shooting at us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some people got killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I guess that was the end of the war from, for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I baked a cake for his birthday once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't, because I can't even imagine where I could have baked it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody must have taken me to the main kitchens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it's a very vague memory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I haven't got the vaguest idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some-- you see, some of it is hearsay, things in my mother told me I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I'm not quite sure whether I remember baking it or whether I remember my mother telling me that I baked it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
